channel.title: Artistry 718 Join today!
channel.description:
Artistry718 is a brand new eco server that right now is in very deep need of players. The server itself is very well coded and has been worked on for over 5 months before going publicly. We've got over 10.000 items and tons and tons of npc's, actually so many that it's gonna blow your mind. There is, in other words, everything that is in the real Runescape since 1 day before EOC, is in our server. Altho we do have items that came out after the EOC on our server.
